thod as a function of cluster mass\nand redshift. We also explore the potential impact of Chandra and XMM-Newton\nfollow-up observations over the next decade on dark energy constraints from new\ncluster surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 May 2017 18:59:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 22:55:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-04"}
