ng a relaxed version of gossip in which it is only necessary\nfor nodes to each learn a specified fraction of the messages in the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 May 2017 15:10:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-29"}
